{"tid":2247361,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我哋輸了 見到拜登團隊完全舉棋不定 就知我哋已經比人將軍無棋了","createTime":"2020-10-17T18:32:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-18T16:33:28.000Z","uid":54373,"like":119,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"18227d46ce350818c2632ebf61cb48214847347f","tid":2247361,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T18:32:18.000Z","msg":"利申: 深藍+拜絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我覺得好失敗，今次照枱面睇已經輸咗<br />\n我偉大祖國玩x完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n見到拜登團隊唔敢出聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n見到朱利亞尼信心爆棚 舉一反三既專訪，已經知答案係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲有班浪費祖國維穩費既5毛PR<br />\n講來講去三福屁既言論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我就知輸硬，真係枱唔起頭做人了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e98fc924c975a9b36aed0bc199a66d1ddf8505f2","tid":2247361,"uid":54373,"like":24,"dislike":1,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T18:34:10.000Z","msg":"希望各位藍絲手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n理性面對事實，得鼓熱血，不斷呃自己<br />\n<br />\n反而令我哋更唔開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"674d3447b842d5b161c6a